{"tid":247683,"cid":4,"subCid":0,"title":"知名外媒流出號稱 iPhone 8 最後一版模型機照片","createTime":"2017-05-18T04:02:45.000Z","updateTime":"2017-05-18T06:06:20.000Z","uid":10788,"like":0,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"e975a3a3119a6f5542a7b15e190af27ac28d17bc","tid":247683,"uid":10788,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-18T04:02:45.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://bit.ly/2rszWR2\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F2rszWR2&d=Ai36%2FzMZEIUB39LyUGzRLZ4f2li5K%2Fs6EGgmwhpeblA%3D&h=cc183f05\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://bit.ly/2rszWR2</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/05/18/120220_aa55dd8ad5a1e43518fe940b4d2cca60.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F05%2F18%2F120220_aa55dd8ad5a1e43518fe940b4d2cca60.jpg&h=de6a69c7&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"a7a722cb9b232b1904b74d197a188ad255feb742","tid":247683,"uid":10788,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-18T04:03:52.000Z","msg":"火熱的諜照又有新進度啦 ! 這次是來自知名科技外媒 BGR 所曝光的一組照片，其指出這組實體模型機的照片為 iPhone 8 最後一個版本的模型機，即意味著這就是 iPhone 8 外觀設計上的最終版本。<br />\n<br />\n若其來源為真，從這組照片中我們可以窺知 iPhone 8 採全螢幕顯示設計、正面無 Home 鍵 ( 可能將指紋辨識功能融入面板中 )、前後皆採 2.5D 曲面玻璃、Lightning 接口、圓弧造型的金屬中框、無 3.5 mm 耳機孔，背面有直式的雙鏡頭。不知道這造型大家滿意否，若有更進一步的消息，本站也會盡快為大家報導 !"},{"pid":"eac76102c5082590e0efb2fc08c2f910a0046d89","tid":247683,"uid":10788,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-18T04:04:03.000Z","msg":"屌<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cf13bbe786a3ff74c647dcf6a058ca56d4b37c2e","tid":247683,"uid":45148,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-18T04:04:53.000Z","msg":"成部s8 咁 <br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cc63cff721e33f0832d463e8a2e33a4aadb07802","tid":247683,"uid":609,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-18T04:13:24.000Z","msg":"個背真係好柒<i